Chapter 1. Admin Guide

   Table of Contents

   1. Overview
   2. Dependencies

        2.1. Kamailio Modules
        2.2. External Libraries or Applications

   3. Parameters

        3.1. protocol (str)
        3.2. timeout_init (int)
        3.3. timeout_read (int)
        3.4. verbosity (int)

   4. Functions

        4.1. lwsc_notify(wsurl, data)
        4.2. lwsc_notify_proto(wsurl, wsproto, data)
